{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>Do not purchase in early access if you want a complete experience</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>It will be rough for a while.</i></u>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Taking inspiration from\u00a0Old School Runescape's custom rulesets popularised on youtube, make meaningful choices, through harsh limitations, that ease through progression in this experimental singleplayer RPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/extras/BoxArt9.png?t=1731589731\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You owe a large debt, and are forced into a virtual prison to pay it off.\u00a0 You can work the debt off slowly through labour, come up with clever mercantile tricks to pay it off faster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/extras/Fishing.gif?t=1731589731\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or get strong and challenge the champion!\u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And if you defeat them all your debts will be wiped clean immediately!\u00a0 But be careful, they're incredibly strong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/extras/Bow.gif?t=1731589731\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every action you perform earns XP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set your own goals, and slowly unlock everything the world has to offer you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/extras/Woodcutting.gif?t=1731589731\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you play you will gain access to new relics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These relics all have hidden bonus effects like being able to walk through fire to access new areas of the map, or passively increasing gathering rates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The relics are incredibly valuable so be sure to find them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/extras/Relics.gif?t=1731589731\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everyone area is chunk locked!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you risk your money exploring the unknown?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or master a small number of known chunks to pay your bills?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/extras/Chunklocked.gif?t=1731589731\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to Cozy Together!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2331890/f8384b88712db21a9b5fc555270ac10f7a077320.jpg"},{"name":"Defeat the Champion!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2331890/52c24a85c5b834034acb02277aa7ca7b685dc333.jpg"}],"total":2},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2331890?t=1731589731","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2331890?t=1731589731","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731589731","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331890/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731589731","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Implied dystopia, nothing bad happens though."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i>Do not purchase in early access if you want a complete experience</i